arial;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font size="2">{!Bug_Log__c.Description__c}</font></span></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">It is&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">{!Bug_Log__c.PrioritySeverity__c}&nbsp;</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">and you wish that it will be resolved on&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">{!Bug_Log__c.Expected_Date__c}</b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">."</span></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2">The support team has received you request.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2">You will receive a confirmation by email when Support team will start the investigation.&nbsp;</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2">We advise you to regulary check the Chatter Tab on your record to follow up actions and questions from Support Team</font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial;"><font size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: right;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; text-align: right;"><font face="Arial, sans-serif" size="2" style="">We assure you that Support Team will do everything they can to solve your request !&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></div>]]></td>
